depositZircuitWeETH().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, by Governance

depositZircuitWeETHs().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, by Governance

withdrawZircuitWeETH().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, Governance and Guardians (for emergency)

withdrawZircuitWeETHs().details: Only delegate callable on Liquidity, Governance and Guardians (for emergency)

depositZircuitWeETH().notice: deposit all WEETH funds to Zircuit and sets approved allowance to max uint256.

depositZircuitWeETHs().notice: deposit all WEETHS funds to Zircuit and sets approved allowance to max uint256.

withdrawZircuitWeETH().notice: withdraw all WEETH funds from Zircuit and sets approved allowance to 0.

withdrawZircuitWeETHs().notice: withdraw all WEETHS funds from Zircuit and sets approved allowance to 0.
